00:35:57.655 --> 00:35:59.740
<i>Robo,</i>

00:35:59.740 --> 00:36:01.701
<i>Asesinato,</i>

00:36:01.701 --> 00:36:05.204
<i>y el Artículo 254, Intento de Asesinato.</i>

00:36:06.414 --> 00:36:09.458
